#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gametype:"
msgstr "Vrsta igre:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arcade, Sport"
msgstr "Arkadna, Šport"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of possible players:"
msgstr "Število možnih igralcev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Ten</para>"
msgstr "<para>Deset</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolf; is a miniature golf game with 2d top-down view. Courses are dynamic, "
"and up to 10 people can play at once in competition."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; je igra mini golfa z 2D pogledom od zgoraj navzdol. Igrišča so "
"dinamična, na tekmovanju pa lahko hkrati igra do 10 ljudi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolf; comes with a tutorial course. <link linkend=\"howto\">Playing this "
"course</link> is the easiest way to get started."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; prihaja z učnim tečajem. <link linkend=\"howto\">Igranje tega tečaja</"
"link> je najlažji način za začetek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the ball into the hole with the least possible hits."
msgstr "Postavite žogo v luknjo z najmanj možnimi udarci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolf;'s game-play is simple. It is the easiest to learn how to play hands-"
"on, and thus a tutorial course is included to guide you through the basics. "
"This chapter will guide you through this tutorial. To start the tutorial, "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tutorial</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Igra &kolf; je preprosta. Najlažje se je naučiti igrati neposredno, zato je "
"vključen tečaj, ki vas vodi skozi osnove. To poglavje vas bo vodilo skozi ta "
"tečaj. Za začetek vadnice izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vadnica</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hitting the Ball"
msgstr "Udarjanje žogice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To aim the ball, either line up the mouse behind the ball so the putter aims "
"in the direction you want to hit it or press one of the &Left; arrow "
"(counterclockwise) or &Right; arrow (clockwise) keys, to rotate the putter."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nameriti žogico, bodisi poravnajte miško za žogico, tako da "
"igralec udari žogico v smer, kamor jo želite udariti, ali pa pritisnite eno "
"od &Left; puščica (v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca) ali &Right; tipke s "
"puščicami (v smeri urinega kazalca) za vrtenje palice za golf."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To rotate the putter more quickly with the keyboard, hold down &Shift; while "
"pressing or holding the arrow keys. To rotate more slowly, hold down &Ctrl;."
msgstr ""
"Za hitrejše vrtenje palice za golf s tipkovnico pridržite &Shift; medtem ko "
"pritiskate ali držite tipke s puščicami. Za počasnejše vrtenje pridržite "
"&Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To hit the ball, press and hold either the &LMB; or &Down; arrow key. The "
"longer you hold down the key or button, the more strength the putt will "
"have. It will take practice to get a good feel for speed."
msgstr ""
"Če želite udariti žogico, pritisnite in držite bodisi &LMB; ali &Down; tipko "
"puščice. Dlje ko držite tipko ali gumb, močnejši bo udarec palice. Za dober "
"občutek za hitrost bo potrebna praksa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To stop the putt while you are still holding moving the putter back in your "
"stroke, press &Esc;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustaviti palico, medtem ko še vedno premikate palico nazaj v "
"zamahu, pritisnite &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hit the ball into the hole to move on to the next."
msgstr "Udarite žogo v luknjo, da nadaljujete na naslednjo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slopes"
msgstr "Pobočja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Slopes are slanted areas of the course that the golf ball rolls down in an "
"expected manner. The light of the golf course is from the upper-left, so the "
"brightest slopes will push the ball towards the upper-left corner of the "
"hole. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see an arrow that points in the "
"direction the slope will roll the ball."
msgstr ""
"Pobočja so poševna območja igrišča, po katerih se žogica za golf kotali "
"navzdol na pričakovan način. Svetloba igrišča za golf je od zgoraj-levo, "
"tako da bodo najsvetlejši pobočji potisnili žogico proti zgornjemu levemu "
"kotu luknje. Izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži informacije</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da "
"vidite puščico, ki kaže v smeri, v katero bo pobočje kotalilo žogico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tutorial hole, hit the ball onto the upward-pointing slope and let "
"it roll into the cup to move onto the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Na tej luknji za vadnico udarite žogico na navzgor usmerjeno pobočje in "
"pustite, da se skotali v skodelico, da se pomakne na naslednjo luknjo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Directions"
msgstr "Navodila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the next hole, experiment with the other kinds of slopes. There are "
"elliptical, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal slopes in &kolf;. Hit the "
"ball into the hole."
msgstr ""
"Na naslednji luknji eksperimentirajte z drugimi vrstami pobočij. V &kolf; "
"obstajajo eliptična, navpična, vodoravna in diagonalna pobočja. Udarite "
"žogico v luknjo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Steepness"
msgstr "Strmina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next tutorial hole has two slopes of differing steepness. If you choose "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, the steepness of the slope will appear "
"as a number from 1-8, where 8 is steepest and 1 is shallowest. Hit the ball "
"into the hole and continue to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja učna luknja ima dve pobočji različnih strmin. Če izberete menijski "
"element <menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"informacije</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, bo strmina pobočja prikazana kot "
"številka od 1 do 8, kjer je 8 najbolj strma in 1 je najpoložnejša. Udarite "
"žogico v luknjo in nadaljujte do naslednje luknje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Walls"
msgstr "Stene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Balls bounce of walls as one would expect them to, with a little bit of "
"dampening. Deflect the ball off the walls and into the cup to advance to the "
"next hole."
msgstr ""
"Žoge se odbijajo od sten, kot bi pričakovali, z malo dušenja. Žogico "
"odvrnite od sten v skodelico, da napredujete do naslednje luknje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107 index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles and Sand"
msgstr "Luže in pesek"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles"
msgstr "Luže"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puddles are blue. When your ball rolls into a puddle, a penalty stroke is "
"added to your score and you must then choose where you want to take your "
"next shot from: either next to the puddle or from the same place as where "
"you just took the last shot."
msgstr ""
"Luže so modre. Ko se vaša žoga zakotali v lužo, se vašemu rezultatu prišteje "
"kazenski udarec in nato morate izbrati, od kod želite izvesti naslednji "
"udarec: ali zraven luže ali z istega mesta, od koder ste zadnjič pravkar "
"udarili."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand"
msgstr "Pesek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand is yellow. Balls roll through sand very slowly."
msgstr "Pesek je rumen. Žoge se kotalijo po pesku zelo počasi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hit the ball around the puddles and through the sand into the hole to "
"continue to the next tutorial hole."
msgstr ""
"Z žogo udarite mimo luž in skozi pesek v luknjo, da nadaljujete do naslednje "
"luknje za vadnico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117 index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windmills"
msgstr "Mlini na veter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Windmills are compound objects with brown border walls and a moving arm on "
"one side. Half-walls create the opening to the windmill, which the black arm "
"swings across. It takes practice to be able to time the stroke of the ball "
"to pass through the opening. Hit the ball through the windmill into the hole "
"to continue."
msgstr ""
"Mlini na veter so sestavljeni predmeti z rjavimi obrobami in premikajočo se "
"roko na eni strani. Polstene ustvarjajo odprtino v mlin na veter, čez "
"katerega niha črna roka. Potrebna je praksa, da lahko merite udarec žoge "
"skozi odprtino. Za nadaljevanje udarite žogo skozi mlin na veter v luknjo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Black Holes"
msgstr "Črne luknje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you hit your ball into a black hole, it is transported to the exit and "
"ejected at the angle of the exit at a speed directly relational to the speed "
"your ball was going. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see which "
"Black Hole goes to which exit and which direction the ball will come out of "
"the exit. The rim around Black Holes are the same color as their "
"corresponding exits. Hit the ball into the black hole, which will then eject "
"the ball into the cup so you can go to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Ko svojo žogico udarite v črno luknjo, se ta premakne do izhoda in izvrže "
"pod kotom izhoda s hitrostjo, ki je neposredno sorazmerna s hitrostjo, s "
"katero se je gibala vaša žogica. Izberite element menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži informacije</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da vidite, katera črna luknja gre do katerega "
"izhoda in v katero smer bo žoga prišla iz izhoda. Rob okoli črnih lukenj je "
"enake barve kot njihovi ustrezni izhodi. Zadenite žogico v črno luknjo, ki "
"jo bo nato vrgla v skodelico, tako da lahko greste do naslednje luknje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125 index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "Floaters"
msgstr "Plovci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Floaters are moving platforms that carry a ball that lands on it. Floaters' "
"speeds vary. This one is a pretty slow floater, but you still must time your "
"shot so you can go over the wall and into the cup."
msgstr ""
"Plovci so premikajoče se platforme, ki nosijo žogico, ki pristane na njih. "
"Hitrosti plovcev so različne. Ta je precej počasen plovec, vendar morate še "
"vedno meriti čas strela, da lahko greste čez steno in v skodelico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bridges"
msgstr "Mostovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bridges are simple - they just lift the ball above the things below them, "
"like slopes, sand, and puddles. They can have brown walls on their perimeter."
msgstr ""
"Mostovi so preprosti - samo dvignejo žogo nad stvari pod njimi, kot so "
"pobočja, pesek in luže. Na obodu imajo lahko rjave stene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's in-depth description of &kolf;'s basic features."
msgstr "Tukaj je poglobljen opis osnovnih funkcij &kolf;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting a Game"
msgstr "Začetek igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start a game, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This opens a dialog "
"where you can configure your new game."
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti igro, izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To odpre pogovorno "
"okno, kjer lahko konfigurirate svojo novo igro."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players Page"
msgstr "Stran igralcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a player to your game, click the <guibutton>New Player</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite svoji igri dodati igralca, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Nov igralec</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "To change the name of the players, change the text in the text boxes."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti imena igralcev, spremenite besedilo v besedilnih poljih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a player, click the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button next to "
"the player's name."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti igralca, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton> "
"poleg igralčevega imena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course Page"
msgstr "Stran igrišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list box "
"on the left of this page. &kolf; comes with many built-in courses that you "
"can play."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati igrišče, kjer želite igrati, kliknite njegov vnos v "
"seznamskem polju na levi strani te strani. &kolf; prihaja s številnimi "
"vgrajenimi igrišči, kjer lahko igrate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
"<guibutton>Add…</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and choose "
"the course file in the file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati igrišče, ki ste ga prenesli ali naredili, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj…</guibutton> na dnu te strani in v pogovornem oknu izberite "
"datoteko igrišča."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options Page"
msgstr "Stran z možnostmi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can choose whether or not this game will be played in "
"<guilabel>Strict mode</guilabel>. In strict mode, there is no undo, moving "
"holes, or editing of the course. This mode is generally for competition. "
"Only in strict mode are high scores kept."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani lahko izberete, ali se bo ta igra igrala v <guilabel>Strogem "
"načinu</guilabel> ali ne. V strogem načinu ni razveljavitev, premikanja "
"lukenj ali urejanja igrišča. Ta način je na splošno namenjen tekmovanju. "
"Samo v strogem načinu se ohranjajo visoke ocene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saved Games"
msgstr "Shranjene igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolf; can keep a history of your rounds that are still in progress and save "
"them to disk so you can load them and play them later. Saved games include "
"the current hole, names and colors of all players in game, and the scores of "
"the players."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; lahko vodi zgodovino vaših rund, ki še potekajo, in jih shrani na "
"disk, da jih lahko naložite in predvajate pozneje. Shranjene igre "
"vključujejo trenutno luknjo, imena in barve vseh igralcev v igri ter "
"rezultate igralcev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Your Game"
msgstr "Shranjevanje vaše igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To save your game while still playing, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. If you "
"have not saved a game on this game before, you will be prompted for the file "
"to save to."
msgstr ""
"Če želite igro shraniti med igranjem, izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani igro</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Če v tej igri še niste shranili igre, boste pozvani, da vnesete "
"datoteko, v katero želite shraniti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading Your Game"
msgstr "Nalaganje vaše igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To load the game that you saved, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. You can "
"then choose the saved game to open."
msgstr ""
"Če želite naložiti igro, ki ste jo shranili, izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži…</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Nato lahko izberete shranjeno igro, ki jo želite odpreti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practicing"
msgstr "Vadba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a few features that make practicing your golf easier. These "
"features are not enabled during strict mode."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja nekaj funkcij, ki olajšajo vadbo golfa. Te funkcije niso omogočene v "
"strogem načinu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo"
msgstr "Razveljavi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To undo a bad shot, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Undo Shot</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite razveljaviti slab strel, izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi strel</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Holes"
msgstr "Preklopne luknje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu contains many menu items for switching to "
"different holes that are quite self explanatory. See the <link linkend=\"go-"
"menu\"><guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu reference</link>."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> vsebuje veliko postavk menija za preklapljanje "
"med različnimi luknjami, ki so povsem razumljive. Oglejte si <link linkend="
"\"go-menu\"><guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> referenco menija</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Putting Options"
msgstr "Možnosti udarjanja s palico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolf; has a few ways to putt. The basic putting method is <link linkend="
"\"hitting\">described above</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; ima nekaj načinov udarjanja žogic. Osnovna metoda udarjanja s palico "
"je <link linkend=\"hitting\">opisana zgoraj</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse is enabled by default. This means that whenever the mouse is "
"moved, the putter aligns to the line between the mouse and ball."
msgstr ""
"Miška je privzeto omogočena. To pomeni, da se vsakič, ko premaknete miško, "
"se palica za golf poravna s črto med miško in žogico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you prefer to only use the keyboard and arrow keys, you can disable mouse "
"putting by unchecking the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Če raje uporabljate samo tipkovnico in puščične tipke, lahko onemogočite "
"udarjanja z miško tako, da počistite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči miško za "
"premikanje palice za golf</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Putting"
msgstr "Napredno udarjanje s palico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Advanced putting can be enabled by checking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Advanced "
"Putting</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This putting mode is slightly "
"more challenging than the regular click-and-hold mode, and can be used with "
"either the mouse or keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Napredno udarjanje s palico lahko omogočite tako, da označite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči "
"napredno udarjanje</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Ta način udarjanja je "
"nekoliko zahtevnejši od običajnega načina klikni in drži in ga je mogoče "
"uporabljati z miško ali tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "To putt in this mode:"
msgstr "Če želite udariti s palico v tem načinu:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key once to begin the swing. The putting "
"indicator will appear, and the strength gauge will start filling up with a "
"color, which changes as the gauge fills up."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ali pritisnite gumb &Down; tipko s puščico enkrat za začetek "
"zamaha. Prikaže se indikator udarjanja in merilnik moči se bo začel polniti "
"z barvo, ki se spreminja, ko se merilnik polni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key when the strength gauge has filled up "
"the amount that you want. The farther around the circle the strength gauge "
"has filled up, the stronger the putt will be. It takes practice to be able "
"to get the correct strength on putts."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ali pritisnite gumb &Down; tipko s puščico, ko merilnik moči "
"napolni želeno količino. Dlje kot se merilec moči napolni okoli kroga, "
"močnejši bo udarec s palico. Potrebna je praksa, da lahko dosežete pravo moč "
"pri udarcih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After this, the color in the putting indicator will start to wind down back "
"to where it started."
msgstr ""
"Po tem se bo barva v indikatorju udarcev začela zmanjševati do tam, kjer se "
"je začela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key again when the strength-indicator is as "
"close as possible to the center line of the putting indicator."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ali pritisnite gumb &Down; znova pritisnite tipko s puščico, ko je "
"indikator moči čim bližje srednji črti indikatorja udarca."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The closer the final click (or key press) is, the more true the putt is to "
"the original line."
msgstr ""
"Bližje kot je končni klik (ali pritisk na tipko), bolj je udarec podoben "
"prvotni liniji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Game Menu"
msgstr "Meni igre"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start a new game."
msgstr "Začni novo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naloži…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Load a previously saved game."
msgstr "Naloži prej shranjeno igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Course</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani igrišče</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the current course using its current file name."
msgstr "Shrani trenutno igrišče z njegovim trenutnim imenom datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Course As…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani igrišče kot…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a file dialog allowing you to <action>save the current course using a "
"new file name.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Odprite pogovorno okno datoteke, v katerem lahko <action>shranite trenutno "
"igrišče z novim imenom datoteke.</action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani igro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Save the current game</action> with the last saved game filename, or "
"under a filename you specify if you have not saved the game yet."
msgstr ""
"<action>Shrani trenutno igro</action> z zadnjim shranjenim imenom datoteke "
"igre ali pod imenom datoteke, ki ga določite, če igre še niste shranili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Game As…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani igro kot…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open a file dialog allowing you to <action>save the current game with a "
"filename of your choice.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno datoteke, v katerem lahko <action>shranite trenutno "
"igro z imenom datoteke po svoji izbiri.</action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>End Game</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&End;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Končaj igro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>End the current game, without closing</action> &kolf;."
msgstr "<action>Končaj trenutno igro brez zapiranja</action> &kolf;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show High Scores</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži najboljše rezultate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the high score table."
msgstr "Prikaži tabelo z najboljšimi rezultati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>About Course…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>O igrišču…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show name, author, and number of holes of the course."
msgstr "Pokaži ime, avtorja in število lukenj igrišča."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quit</action> &kolf;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kolf;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Hole Menu"
msgstr "Meni Luknje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Switch to editing mode</action> to edit the current hole."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopite v način urejanja</action>, da uredite trenutno luknjo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Create a new hole.</action> (Only while editing.)"
msgstr "<action>Ustvari novo luknjo.</action> (Samo med urejanjem.)"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Del;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Del;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Počisti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Remove all objects from the current hole.</action> (Only while "
"editing.)"
msgstr ""
"<action>Odstrani vse predmete iz trenutne luknje.</action> (Samo med "
"urejanjem.)"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reset</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponastavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Reset the current hole to its starting position</action>, so that "
"you can start over."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ponastavi trenutno luknjo na začetni položaj</action>, da lahko "
"začnete znova."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži informacije</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show information about objects on the current hole."
msgstr "Prikaži informacije o predmetih na trenutni luknji."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo Shot</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi strel</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo the last shot you made."
msgstr "Razveljavi zadnji strel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Go Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pojdi"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Switch to Hole</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preklopi na luknjo</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Go directly to another hole within the course.</action> A list of "
"the hole numbers allows you to choose which hole you wish to go to."
msgstr ""
"<action>Pojdite neposredno na drugo luknjo znotraj igrišča.</action> Seznam "
"številk lukenj vam omogoča, da izberete, na katero luknjo želite iti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Hole</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednja luknja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next hole."
msgstr "Pojdi do naslednje luknje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Hole</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnja luknja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous hole."
msgstr "Pojdi na prejšnjo luknjo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Home;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>First Hole</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Home;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prva luknja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the first hole in the course."
msgstr "Pojdi do prve luknje na igrišču."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&End;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Last Hole</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&End;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zadnja luknja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the last hole in the course."
msgstr "Pojdi do zadnje luknje na igrišču."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Random Hole</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naključna luknja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to a random hole from the current course."
msgstr "Pojdi na naključno luknjo s trenutnega igrišča."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolf; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections about the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> "
"and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</"
"ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals with these additional entries:"
msgstr ""
"&kolf; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z nastavitvami</"
"ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">meni "
"Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove s temi dodatnimi vnosi:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči miško za premikanje "
"palice za golf</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow the use of the mouse to move the putter."
msgstr "Dovolite uporabo miške za premikanje palice za golf."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Advanced Putting</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči napredno udarjanje s "
"palico</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Enable the advanced putting mode</action>, as described in <link "
"linkend=\"advanced-putting\">its own section</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogočite napredni način udarjanja s palico</action>, kot je opisano "
"v <link linkend=\"advanced-putting\">lastnem razdelku</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Putter Guideline</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži vodilo za palico za golf</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle on and off the putter guideline."
msgstr "Vklapljanje in izklapljanje vodila za palico za golf."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj zvoke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle on and off the sound effects."
msgstr "Vklop in izklop zvočnih učinkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable All Dialog Boxes</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omogoči vsa pogovorna okna</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Re-enable any dialog boxes that you disabled by clicking on <guilabel>Do not "
"show this message again</guilabel> or similar."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno omogočite vsa pogovorna okna, ki ste jih onemogočili s klikom na "
"<guilabel>Ne prikaži več tega sporočila</guilabel> ali podobno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tutorial</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vadnica</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start the tutorial course of &kolf;."
msgstr "Začnite vadnico tečaja &kolf;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. At this moment &kolf; features only one theme."
msgstr "Ne. V tem trenutku ima &kolf; samo eno temo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Yes. Use the directional keys to control the putter."
msgstr "Da. Uporabite smerne tipke, da upravljate s palico za golf."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne morem ugotoviti, kaj naj naredim tukaj! Ali obstajajo namigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kolf; does not have a hint feature."
msgstr "Ne. &kolf; nima funkcije namiga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to design my own golf course. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim oblikovati lastno igrišče za golf. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, you can. To enter the edit mode use the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item. Click <link linkend=\"creating\">here</link> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Da lahko. Za vstop v način urejanja uporabite "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem> Uredi</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> element menija. Kliknite <link linkend=\"creating"
"\">tukaj</link> za več podrobnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course Editor"
msgstr "Urednik igrišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolf; comes with a versatile editor for its course file format. Courses can "
"have any number of holes, and there is no limiting the creativity of the "
"course designer."
msgstr ""
"&kolf; prihaja z vsestranskim urejevalnikom za svoj format datoteke igrišča. "
"Igrišča imajo lahko poljubno število lukenj in ustvarjalnost oblikovalca "
"igrišča ni omejena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a New Course"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novega igrišča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new course, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Go to the "
"<guilabel>Course</guilabel> page of the dialog, and choose the "
"<guilabel>Create New</guilabel> course. Make sure that, under the "
"<guilabel>Options</guilabel> page of the dialog, <guilabel>Strict mode</"
"guilabel> is unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo igrišče, izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Pojdite na stran <guilabel>Igrišče</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu "
"in izberite <guilabel>Ustvari novo</guilabel> igrišče. Prepričajte se, da "
"pod stranjo <guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel> pogovornega okna <guilabel>Strogi "
"način</guilabel> ni označen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To play this new course later, click the <guibutton>Add…</guibutton> button "
"to add the course to your list of courses."
msgstr ""
"Če želite igrati na tem novem igrišču pozneje, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj…</guibutton>, da dodate igrišče na svoj seznam igrišč."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Holes"
msgstr "Dodajanje lukenj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to the edit mode using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item to add a new hole at the end of the course."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite v način urejanja z menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Izberite menijski "
"element <menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da dodate novo luknjo na koncu igrišča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can restore a hole to a blank state, similar to when it was first "
"created, by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Luknjo lahko povrnete v prazno stanje, podobno tistemu, ko je bila prvič "
"ustvarjena, tako da izberete menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Počisti</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two items will appear on new holes: a cup, and a white ball. The white ball "
"marks where players' balls start the hole."
msgstr ""
"Na novih luknjah se bosta pojavila dva predmeta: skodelica in bela krogla. "
"Bela krogla označuje, kje žogice igralcev začnejo luknjo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Basics"
msgstr "Osnove urejanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The basic building block of &kolf; courses is the <quote>object</quote>. "
"Holes are made up of a bunch of objects. Objects can be moved to any "
"location, and the different kinds of objects each have different properties "
"you can set."
msgstr ""
"Osnovni gradnik &kolf; igrišča je <quote>predmet</quote>. Luknje so "
"sestavljene iz množice predmetov. Predmete je mogoče premakniti na katero "
"koli lokacijo, različne vrste predmetov pa imajo različne lastnosti, ki jih "
"lahko nastavite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start editing a hole, toggle the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, or press the pencil "
"icon on the toolbar. To leave editing mode, uncheck this menu item (or the "
"toolbar icon)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti urejati luknjo, preklopite menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Luknja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali pritisnite ikono svinčnika v orodni vrstici. Če želite "
"zapustiti način urejanja, počistite to menijsko postavko (ali ikono v orodni "
"vrstici)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Objects"
msgstr "Dodajanje predmetov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a new object to the course, choose its name in the list box labeled "
"<guilabel>Add object:</guilabel>. The object will appear in the center of "
"the course."
msgstr ""
"Če želite igrišču dodati nov predmet, izberite njegovo ime v seznamskem "
"polju z oznako <guilabel>Dodaj predmet:</guilabel>. Predmet se bo pojavil v "
"središču igrišča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bridges and signs will cover up new objects if they were already in the "
"center of the hole."
msgstr ""
"Mostovi in znaki bodo prekrili nove predmete, če so bili že v središču "
"luknje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving and Resizing Objects"
msgstr "Premikanje in spreminjanje velikosti predmetov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move your mouse cursor over the object that you want to move, and the mouse "
"cursor will change to a hand cursor. Then click and drag the object to where "
"you want it."
msgstr ""
"Premaknite kazalec miške nad predmet, ki ga želite premakniti, in kazalec "
"miške se bo spremenil v kazalec roke. Nato kliknite in povlecite predmet na "
"želeno mesto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puddles, sand, floaters, bridges, and signs can be resized by dragging the "
"small circle at their lower-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Luže, pesek, plovci, mostovi in znaki lahko spremenijo velikost tako, da "
"povlečete majhen krog v njihovem spodnjem desnem kotu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Walls can be moved by clicking and dragging their endpoints, or you can move "
"the whole wall by clicking and dragging on the middle part of the wall as "
"normal."
msgstr ""
"Stene lahko premikate tako, da kliknete in povlečete njihove končne točke, "
"ali pa premaknete celotno steno tako, da kliknete in povlečete srednji del "
"stene kot običajno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objects' Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve predmetov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Objects' properties can be changed in the area at the lower-right corner of "
"the &kolf; window. To edit an object, move your mouse cursor over it until "
"the cursor changes to the hand cursor. Then click. Various controls for that "
"object will appear in the lower-right corner of the &kolf; window."
msgstr ""
"Lastnosti predmetov lahko spremenite v območju v spodnjem desnem kotu &kolf; "
"okno. Če želite urediti predmet, premikajte kazalec miške nad njim, dokler "
"se kazalec ne spremeni v kazalec roke. Nato kliknite. Različni kontrolniki "
"za ta predmet se bodo pojavili v spodnjem desnem kotu &kolf; okna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Hole Settings"
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve lukenj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit general hole settings, click an area of the hole that is not covered "
"by an object. When this is possible, the cursor will be the normal pointer "
"cursor."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti splošne nastavitve luknje, kliknite območje luknje, ki ga "
"ne pokriva noben predmet. Če je to mogoče, bo kazalec kar običajni kazalec."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course name:"
msgstr "Ime igrišča:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the name that is shown in the <guilabel>New Game</guilabel> dialog "
"and in the <guilabel>Course Information</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"To je ime, ki je prikazano v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Nova igra</guilabel> "
"in pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Informacije o igrišču</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course author:"
msgstr "Avtor igrišča:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the author name that is shown in the <guilabel>Course Information</"
"guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"To je ime avtorja, ki je prikazano v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Informacije o "
"igrišču</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid "Par:"
msgstr "Par:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid "The par of the hole."
msgstr "Par luknje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximum:"
msgstr "Največ:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum number of strokes a player can take on the hole."
msgstr "Največje število udarcev, ki jih igralec lahko odigra na tej luknji."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show border walls"
msgstr "Prikaži mejne stene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whether or not to show walls around the border of the hole."
msgstr "Ali želite prikazati stene okoli roba luknje ali ne."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the type of the slope - <guilabel>Vertical</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Horizontal</guilabel>, <guilabel>Diagonal</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Opposite Diagonal</guilabel>, <guilabel>Circular</guilabel>. "
"Diagonal and opposite diagonal slopes are triangles, while circular slopes "
"are circles. Vertical and horizontal slopes are rectangles of course."
msgstr ""
"Izberite vrsto naklona pobočja - <guilabel>Navpično</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Vodoravno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Diagonalno</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Nasprotno diagonalno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Krožno</guilabel>. "
"Diagonalna in nasprotna diagonalna pobočja so trikotniki, krožna pobočja pa "
"krogi. Navpična in vodoravna pobočja sta seveda pravokotnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reverse direction"
msgstr "Obratna smer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether or not to reverse the slant of the slope. For example, consider an "
"elliptical slope (a circular slope). When it is not reversed, it pushes "
"balls outward like a mound. When it is reversed, it sucks balls inward like "
"a hole."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali obrniti naklon pobočja. Na primer, upoštevajte eliptično "
"pobočje (krožno pobočje). Ko ni obrnjeno, potisne kroglice navzven kot "
"krtina. Ko je obrnjena, posrka kroglice navznoter kot luknja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unmovable"
msgstr "Nepremično"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whether or not this can be moved by other objects, like floaters."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali je to mogoče premakniti z drugimi predmeti, kot so "
"plovci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a floater overlaps with this object at any point on this path, and the "
"slope is large and thus won't move the floater, you <emphasis>must</"
"emphasis> make the slope <guilabel>Unmovable</guilabel>, or &kolf; will "
"suffer poor performance!"
msgstr ""
"Če se plovec prekriva s tem predmetom na kateri koli točki te poti in je "
"naklon velik in zato ne premakne plovca, <emphasis>morate</emphasis> "
"narediti naklon <guilabel>Nepremakljiv</guilabel> ali bo &kolf; deloval "
"počasi!"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grade:"
msgstr "Ocena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the grade (steepness) of the slope by moving the slider so the grade "
"moves towards 0 or 8, where 8 is steepest and 0 is flat. Steeper slopes push "
"the ball more."
msgstr ""
"Izberite naklon (strmino) pobočja tako, da premaknete drsnik, tako da se "
"naklon premakne proti 0 ali 8, kjer je 8 najbolj strm in 0 ravninski. "
"Strmejši klanci bolj potiskajo žogo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles and Sand have the same configuration options as each other."
msgstr "Luže in pesek imata enake konfiguracijske možnosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable show/hide"
msgstr "Omogoči prikaz/skrij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking this enables the flashing of this puddle or sand."
msgstr "Če to preverite, omogočite utripanje te luže ali peska."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more towards <guilabel>Fast</guilabel> the slider is, the faster the "
"puddle or sand flashes."
msgstr ""
"Bolj kot je drsnik proti <guilabel>Hitro</guilabel>, hitreje utripa luža ali "
"pesek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bridges, Windmills, Floaters, and Signs"
msgstr "Mostovi, mlini na veter, plovci in znaki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bridges, windmills, floaters, and signs all have similar settings for "
"configuring on which sides there are border walls. To show the wall on a "
"side, check the check box for that side."
msgstr ""
"Mostovi, mlini na veter, plovci in znaki imajo podobne nastavitve za "
"konfiguracijo, na katerih straneh so mejni zidovi. Če želite steno prikazati "
"ob strani, potrdite polje za to stran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also some more specific options for windmills, floaters, and signs."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo tudi nekatere bolj specifične možnosti za vetrnice, plovce in "
"znake."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windmill on top"
msgstr "Mlin na veter na vrhu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether or not the black windmill arm is on bottom or top - the default is "
"that it is on the top. The two half-walls will always be with the arm. Note "
"that you cannot enable a border wall on the side that the arm is."
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali je črna roka vetrnice na dnu ali na vrhu - privzeto je, "
"da je na vrhu. Dve polsteni bosta vedno z roko. Upoštevajte, da ne morete "
"omogočiti obrobne stene na strani, kjer je roka."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed"
msgstr "Hitrost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more towards <guilabel>Fast</guilabel> the slider is, the faster the "
"black windmill arm moves."
msgstr ""
"Bolj kot je drsnik proti <guilabel>Hitro</guilabel>, hitreje se premika črna "
"roka vetrnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The path the floater moves along is shown by the wall it's connected to."
msgstr ""
"Pot, po kateri se premika plovec, je prikazana s steno, s katero je povezan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving speed"
msgstr "Hitrost premikanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more towards <guilabel>Fast</guilabel> the slider is, the faster the "
"floater moves. If the slider is all the way at the <guilabel>Slow</guilabel> "
"end, the floater will stop."
msgstr ""
"Bolj kot je drsnik proti <guilabel>Hitro</guilabel>, hitreje se premika "
"plovec. Če je drsnik povsem na koncu <guilabel>Počasi</guilabel>, se bo "
"plovec ustavil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signs"
msgstr "Znaki"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sign HTML:"
msgstr "Podpišite HTML:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter any valid &HTML; here. For example, entering <userinput>Hit it "
"&lt;i&gt;softly&lt;/i&gt; towards the slope!</userinput> will create the "
"text <quote>Hit it <emphasis>softly</emphasis> towards the slope!</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesete lahko poljuben veljaven &HTML; tukaj Na primer, če vnesete "
"<userinput>Hit it &lt;i&gt;nežno&lt;/i&gt; proti pobočju!</userinput> bo "
"ustvarilo besedilo <quote>Udari <emphasis>nežno</emphasis> proti pobočju!</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge in licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kolf;"
msgstr "&kolf;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kolf; copyright 2001, 2002 &Jason.Katz-Brown;"
msgstr "&kolf; avtorske pravice 2001, 2002 &Jason.Katz-Brown;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:783
